---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — Social Text Toolkit" description="Privacy Policy for Social Text Toolkit. We do not collect, store, or share any personal data. All tools work entirely in your browser.">
  <article class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-8"><em>Last updated: June 17, 2026</em></p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">Our Commitment to Privacy</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Social Text Toolkit ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you visit our website at socialtexttoolkit.com (the "Service").
    </p>
    <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
      <strong class="text-[var(--text-primary)]">The short version: We don't collect, store, or share any personal data. Period.</strong>
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">Information We Do NOT Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-[var(--text-secondary)] space-y-2 mb-4">
      <li><strong class="text-[var(--text-primary)]">Personal identification information</strong> — No names, email addresses, phone numbers, or any other PII.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-[var(--text-primary)]">Account data</strong> — We have no user accounts, no registration, and no login system.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-[var(--text-primary)]">Payment information</strong> — We have no paid features, no subscriptions, and no payment processing.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-[var(--text-primary)]">Usage analytics that identify you</strong> — We may use basic, anonymized analytics (such as page view counts) but never track individual users.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-[var(--text-primary)]">Cookies for tracking</strong> — We do not use tracking cookies, advertising cookies, or third-party cookies.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">Local Storage</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Our Service uses your browser's localStorage to save your preferences and data entirely on your device:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-[var(--text-secondary)] space-y-2 mb-4">
      <li><strong class="text-[var(--text-primary)]">Favorites</strong> — Symbols, kaomoji, and text snippets you save are stored in your browser.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-[var(--text-primary)]">Copy history</strong> — Recently copied items for quick re-access.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-[var(--text-primary)]">Theme preference</strong> — Your light/dark mode choice.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
      This data never leaves your browser. You can clear it at any time through your browser settings or by clearing site data. We cannot access, view, or recover this data.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">How Our Tools Work</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
      All text transformation, symbol lookup, image generation (text-to-image tool), and preview functionality runs entirely in your browser using client-side JavaScript. The text you type into our tools never leaves your device and is never transmitted to any server.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Our Service is hosted on Cloudflare Pages, which may collect basic, anonymized infrastructure-level data (such as request logs) as part of their standard service. Cloudflare's privacy practices are documented at <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" class="text-brand-500 hover:text-brand-600 underline" rel="noopener noreferrer">cloudflare.com/privacypolicy</a>.
    </p>
    <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
      We load the Inter font family from Google Fonts. Google's privacy practices for Fonts are documented at <a href="https://developers.google.com/fonts/faq/privacy" class="text-brand-500 hover:text-brand-600 underline" rel="noopener noreferrer">developers.google.com/fonts/faq/privacy</a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Our Service is not directed to children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. Since we do not collect any personal information from anyone, this applies universally.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">GDPR &amp; CCPA Compliance</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Because we do not collect, process, or store any personal data, we are inherently compliant with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA). There is no personal data to access, delete, or opt out of processing.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
      If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-500 hover:text-brand-600 underline">Contact page</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
